==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Brancher
<hw>Branch"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>That
which shoots forth branches; one who shows growth in various
directions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Falconry)</fld> <def>A young hawk when it begins to
leave the nest and take to the branches.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Branchery</ent>⟦br⟧
